i) (denoted with reference number 128) retrieving at least one set of shaping target criteria for the shaping tool 126;
ii) (denoted with reference number 130) defining at least one starting geometry for the shaping tool 126;
iii) (denoted with reference number 132) generating a set of shaping parameters comprising at least one shape geometry parameter of the starting geometry;
